## States

Define every state each screen can be in. AI agents frequently miss edge-case states, so be thorough.

> Full state matrix: `packages/specs/{{name}}-states.md`

### {{titleCase name}}

| State    | Condition                        | What the User Sees                          |
| -------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| Idle     | Initial load, no interaction yet | Clean default UI                            |
| Loading  | Async operation in progress      | Spinner/skeleton, inputs disabled            |
| Empty    | No data available                | Empty state illustration with CTA           |
| Success  | Operation completed              | Success feedback (toast, redirect, message) |
| Error    | Server returned an error         | Inline error banner with message            |

